---
import { storeUrl } from "../site";
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden px-8 pt-[clamp(44px,5.5vw,80px)] pb-[clamp(56px,6vw,88px)]"
  style="background:radial-gradient(125% 110% at 82% -10%, #EDF3E9 0%, #DEE9D8 52%, #CFDCC9 100%)"
>
  <div
    class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-[1200px] items-center gap-[clamp(40px,5vw,72px)]"
    style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(360px,1fr))"
  >
    <div>
      <h1
        class="text-[clamp(40px,6vw,68px)] font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-[-0.01em] text-ink-strong"
      >
        让眼睛，<br />休憩片刻
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-[22px] max-w-[520px] text-[clamp(17px,1.5vw,20px)] leading-[1.7] text-body">
        长时间盯着屏幕，眼睛会悄悄变累。「憩目」按你的用眼节奏，温柔地提醒你抬起头、望向远方——不催促，不打断，只是轻轻提醒。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-[30px] flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3.5">
        <a
          href={storeUrl}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-block leading-none transition-opacity hover:opacity-[.88]"
        >
          <img
            src="https://get.microsoft.com/images/zh-cn%20dark.svg"
            alt="从 Microsoft Store 下载"
            class="block h-[58px] w-auto"
          />
        </a>
        <a
          href="#demo"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-[10px] border-[1.5px] border-[#283c32]/20 bg-white/50 px-[26px] py-[15px] text-[17px] font-semibold text-ink transition-colors hover:bg-white/85"
          >在线体验一下</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[22px] flex flex-wrap items-center gap-[22px]">
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-[7px] whitespace-nowrap text-[14px] font-semibold text-muted-2"
        >
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M16.365 1.43c0 1.14-.42 2.2-1.13 2.99-.83.94-2.2 1.66-3.32 1.57-.14-1.09.44-2.26 1.12-3 .78-.85 2.19-1.5 3.33-1.56zM20.9 17.02c-.55 1.27-.82 1.84-1.53 2.97-.99 1.57-2.38 3.52-4.1 3.54-1.53.01-1.92-1-4-1-2.07.01-2.5 1.01-4.03.99-1.72-.02-3.03-1.79-4.02-3.36-2.76-4.4-3.05-9.56-1.35-12.31 1.21-1.95 3.12-3.09 4.91-3.09 1.83 0 2.98 1 4.49 1 1.47 0 2.36-1 4.48-1 1.6 0 3.3.87 4.5 2.38-3.96 2.17-3.31 7.82.2 9.55z"
            ></path></svg
          >Mac 版开发中
        </span>
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-[7px] whitespace-nowrap text-[14px] font-semibold text-muted-2"
        >
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M17.6 9.48l1.84-3.18a.4.4 0 00-.69-.4l-1.87 3.23a11.4 11.4 0 00-9.76 0L5.25 5.9a.4.4 0 10-.69.4L6.4 9.48A10.8 10.8 0 001 18h22a10.8 10.8 0 00-5.4-8.52zM7 15.25a1.25 1.25 0 110-2.5 1.25 1.25 0 010 2.5zm10 0a1.25 1.25 0 110-2.5 1.25 1.25 0 010 2.5z"
            ></path></svg
          >Android 版开发中
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] tracking-[.01em] text-muted-2">
        无遥测 · 不收集个人数据 · 数据只留在本机
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="animate-floaty relative">
      <div
        class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#283c32]/[0.08] shadow-[0_44px_96px_-34px_rgba(30,50,42,.5)]"
      >
        <img src="/assets/stats-light.png" alt="憩目 应用界面：用眼数据与统计" class="block w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
